snippet.title: Blast Zone! Tournament - Release Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The competitive bomb-throwing arena game will be leaving Early Access and launching on PS4, Xbox One, and Steam on February 28.

Watch more trailers here!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vvB2wiDUDdA&list=PLaQokWZfgbynLRhV7HigqcfVAzsNB-t6b&index=1
